&quot;I think most everyone would say that the only thing that really needs nerfing in EQ is Vah Shir, they eat food and drink things too slowly compared to where they should be.&quot;
<br />

<br />
While their sheer size would indicate a need for more food/drink intake than some of the smaller classes, their increased metabolism covers that well.  In going with the metabolism of real cats though, they don't eat or drink all that much...especially drink since they are adapted for arid climates.
