				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Why are bards so uber???<a name="29264"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 22 04 1:45 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span><blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">Why do bards bank their epic so late ? 
<br />
Because it is uber ? 
<br />
or because bard items are not so good ?</span></blockquote>
<br />
It's damage/delay ratio sucks.  Better weapons are Bazaar purchable.  Bard melee is bad to begin with, but couple it with the fact that we are basically stuck with this thing in our offhand and that only makes it worse.
<br />

<br />
But it is still definately uber.  80% boost to just about everything we do.  I think you'd be hard pressed to find an item - anywhere - that does that for another class.
<br />
Plus it's got a sweet proc.  40 ATK that stacks with everything is very very nice.
<br />

<br />
So why is banked so late?
<br />
Simply because you have to be Elemental/Time or higher to have any prayer of finding same or better instrument/singing mods.  And you have to have a rare drop from Inny in Time before you can really replace the proc.</span></td>
