				<td colspan="2"><span>Someone else mentioned it.
<br />
1.  Bards solo better than any other class in the game.  
<br />
2.  Bards offer more to groups than any other class in the game.
<br />

<br />
That's it.  Your uber when you solo, and your uber when you group.  Alot of classes would be happy being able to handle just one of those.
<br />
It's only a matter of time before you/we bards get nerfed more.  The fact that its very risky to AE kite or anything is beside the point.  They will instantly say that it's risky for them to try and solo a single dark blue mob, much less an massive pack of them.  Which is true in the case of any melee class.  Sooo, enjoy it while it lasts, cause I am sure SoE will gank bards in some fashion.  We've already seen the first nerf to the AE AA.  Expect more.<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-12.gif" border="0" alt="Mad" hspace="2" /></span></td>
